						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Vīrarājēndradēva. Year 4+5: A.D. 1215.</hi></p>						

						<p>Portions damaged. Gift of some money <hi rend="italic">(achchu)</hi> for a twilight lamp in the temple of Tirumunnai-Āḷuḍaiyār, by Daruman of chiruttalai vēṭṭuvar community from Teṉkarai Koḍuvēli in Vaḍaparisāra-nāḍu. On accepting the money as deposit, Āḷavatta Bhaṭṭan, a <hi rend="italic">śiva-brāhmaṇa</hi> of the temple agreed to maintain the lamp.</p>						

